            "title_1": "What You Can Make",
            "raw_content_1": "<p><strong>Intimate</strong></p><ul><li>1 bridal bouquet </li><li>5 bridesmaids bouquets</li><li>10 boutonnieres </li></ul><p><strong>Small</strong></p><ul><li>1 bridal bouquet </li><li>5 bridesmaids bouquets</li><li>10 boutonnieres </li><li>5 Centerpieces</li></ul><p><strong>Medium </strong></p><ul><li>1 bridal bouquet </li><li>6 bridesmaids bouquets</li><li>10 boutonnieres </li><li>10 Centerpieces</li></ul><p><strong>Large</strong></p><ul><li>1 bridal bouquet </li><li>6 bridesmaids bouquets</li><li>12 boutonnieres </li><li>3 Corsages</li><li>1 Single Arch Arrangement </li><li>12 Centerpieces</li></ul><p><strong>Grand</strong></p><ul><li>1 bridal bouquet </li><li>10 bridesmaids bouquets</li><li>15 boutonnieres </li><li>5 Corsages</li><li>Double Arch Arrangement </li><li>15 Centerpieces</li></ul>",
